{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3118160/extras/Floodcore_Environment.gif?t=1724669112\" /><br><br>Floodcore is a <strong>puzzle adventure game</strong> in which you explore an ancient civilization in a flooded world, and discover a mysterious power to overcome the temple's challenges.<br><br>This game is a vertical slice made by <strong>5 French students</strong> within 8 months as a graduation project. You can expect <strong>15 to 30 minutes of gameplay</strong> depending on your affinity with puzzle games and your sense of spatial awareness in a 3D environment.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3118160/extras/Floodcore_Swap.gif?t=1724669112\" /><br><br>Your power allows you to <strong>swap</strong> positions with specific objects in the world, or swap them together. Delve further into the temple and solve puzzles that require you to become a part of them.<br><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3118160/extras/Floodcore_Puzzles.gif?t=1724669112\" /><br><br>Each area expands on the swap mechanic and makes you use it in different ways.<br>Some will challenge you and require you to anticipate several moves ahead, while others will need you to figure out every possibility, and there are often several different solutions for them!<br><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3118160/extras/Floodcore_Explore.gif?t=1724669112\" /><br><br>You will discover multiple ruins laid by an ancient civilisation, each with its own visuals and purpose.<br>From the temple's surface to its underground, all the way to a luxuriant garden, you will experience each area differently with their puzzles and atmosphere.<br><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3118160/extras/Floodcore_Atmosphere.gif?t=1724669112\" /><br><br>At any point in time, you can take a step back and enjoy the calm atmosphere with the sound of waves, birds, wind and waterfalls.","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3118160/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1724669112","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3118160/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1724669112","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3118160/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1724669112","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3118160/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1724669112","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3118160/extras/Floodcore_Environment.gif?t=1724669112\" /><br><br>Floodcore is a <strong>puzzle adventure game</strong> in which you explore an ancient civilization in a flooded world, and discover a mysterious power to overcome the temple's challenges.<br><br>This game is a vertical slice made by <strong>5 French students</strong> within 8 months as a graduation project. You can expect <strong>15 to 30 minutes of gameplay</strong> depending on your affinity with puzzle games and your sense of spatial awareness in a 3D environment.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3118160/extras/Floodcore_Swap.gif?t=1724669112\" /><br><br>Your power allows you to <strong>swap</strong> positions with specific objects in the world, or swap them together. Delve further into the temple and solve puzzles that require you to become a part of them.<br><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.ste